data.description: Immaculate 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath two-story home nestled in The Village of Decker Oaks Subdivision off 249, minutes away from 99 Grand Parkway.  Built in 2013, this residence boasts a well-equipped kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space.  Half bath located on first floor.  Five generously sized bedrooms feature walk-in closets.  Primary bath offers double sinks, a soaking tub and separate walk-in shower.  Secondary bathroom includes double sinks and combo tub/shower.  Enjoy family gatherings in the spacious game room. Parking is a breeze in the two-car garage with automatic opener.  Backyard offers an above-ground pool.  Home has solar panels for eco-friendly energy efficiency.  Exercise area and a gated playground a few blocks away within the family-friendly subdivision, offering a safe and enjoyable space for recreation.  Contact the listing agent to schedule your private showing to experience the charm of this well-maintained home.
